com.liquidm.sdk
Class NativeAd

java.lang.Object
  com.liquidm.sdk.NativeAd
All Implemented Interfaces:
Parcelable, Iterable<String>
public class NativeAd
extends Object
implements Iterable<String>, Parcelable

Representation of a native ad. It offers methods to conveniently fetch data in a desired format.
CAUTION: NativeAd data is parcelable with exception of preloaded images.
This allows to pass NativeAd in Intent, but preloaded images must be passed separately, because Intent won't hold so much data.
